  <name>lact</name>
  <summary> Linux AMDGPU Configuration Tool</summary>
  
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      This application allows you to control your AMD GPU on a Linux system.
    </p>
    <p>
      Current features:
    </p>
    <p>
      - Viewing information about the GPU - Power/thermals monitoring - Fan curve control - Overclocking (GPU/VRAM clockspeed, voltage) - Power states configuration
    </p>
  </description>
  
